        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 4. Scyracepon biglobosus n. sp. Scanning Electron Micrograph of paratype male. A. Ventral view of the male; B. Right antennae; C. Right pereopods 1–3; D. Propodus, carpus and merus of pereopod 3; E. Midventral projections of pereomere 6; F. Ventral view of pleon; G. Pleotelson and anal cone. Scale-bars: A = 0.50 mm; B, C, E = 50 um; D = 20 um; F = 80 um; G = 40 um." ;
